&lt;p&gt;In charming Osnabr&uuml;ck&nbsp;stands an 1813 building where you&rsquo;ll find&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;#63&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;World&amp;#8217;s 50 Best Restaurants 2013, 2014 World&amp;#8217;s 50 Best Global Selection, and Michelin 3 Stars &lt;/strong&gt;restaurant&nbsp;La Vie. Chef Thomas B&uuml;hner&rsquo;s menus feature harmonious flavors and textures which are brilliantly executed and enjoyed in an elegantly relaxed dining room. Elegant attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at the La Vie website: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.restaurant-lavie.de/deutsch/opentable-reservierung.html&quot;&gt;http://www.restaurant-lavie.de/deutsch/opentable-reservierung.html&lt;/a&gt; or contact La Vie by phone at +49 5 41 33 11 50 or email at email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:info@restaurant-lavie.de&quot;&gt;info@restaurant-lavie.de&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit. (Online, in the section &ldquo;Besondere W&uuml;nsche an das Restaurant&rdquo;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant La Vie requires a credit card to hold your reservation. A deposit of 100 Euros per guest will be charged to your credit card. This will be applied to your meal. The balance will be due at the completion of your meal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: If not cancelled 24 hours prior to the dining date, the entire deposit will not be returned. If cancelled outside of 24 hours the deposit is fully refunded&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

